stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> initialize
    initialize --> load_context: SA instance created
    load_context --> evaluate_plan: Context loaded successfully
    evaluate_plan --> execute_step: Execution order determined
    execute_step --> emit_trace: Step execution complete
    emit_trace --> complete: All steps executed
    complete --> [*]
    
    note right of initialize
        SA initialization
        Generate sa_id
    end note
    
    note right of load_context
        Load Context object
        Validate context_id
        Check context.status == active
    end note
    
    note right of evaluate_plan
        Parse Plan structure
        Resolve step dependencies
        Build execution graph
    end note
    
    note right of execute_step
        Execute according to agent_role
        Handle tool/LLM/agent executors
        Update step status
    end note
    
    note right of emit_trace
        Write SA events to Trace
        Record step outcomes
        Maintain audit trail
    end note
